HEADWORD: Brin
<hw>Brin</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety> <def>One of
the radiating sticks of a fan. The outermost are larger and longer, and
are called <xex>panaches</xex>.</def> <rj><au>Knight.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

